  <brief_title>Stem Cells Therapy in Advanced Heart Failure</brief_title>
  <official_title>Intra Cardiac Autologous Stem Cells Infusion May Improve Clinical Outcomes in Failing Heart Subjects Refractory to Maximal Drug Therapy and Internal Cardioverter With a Defibrillator (ICD) Recipients</official_title>
  <sponsors>
